### Velocity RGS — Client REST Client mirror
### Use with the "REST Client" VS Code extension (humao.rest-client).
### Authentication: first call `dev/token`, then copy the returned token into @token.

@host = http://localhost:8080
@gameId = aztec-fire
@currency = EUR
@playerId = p-1001
@sessionId = s-2001
@roundId = r-3001
@token = paste-jwt-here
@idempotencyKey = 11111111-2222-4333-8444-555555555555
@traceId = 22222222-3333-4444-8555-666666666666

### Demo: mint a JWT (demo profile only)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/dev/token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerId": "{{playerId}}",
  "sessionId": "{{sessionId}}",
  "currency": "{{currency}}",
  "roles": ["PLAYER", "ADMIN"],
  "ttlMinutes": 60
}

### Wallet — authenticate the player session
POST {{host}}/api/v1/wallet/authenticate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Trace-Id: {{traceId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "playerId": "{{playerId}}" }

### Wallet — read balance
GET {{host}}/api/v1/wallet/balance
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Trace-Id: {{traceId}}

### Wallet — direct debit (Idempotency-Key required)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/wallet/debit
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{idempotencyKey}}
X-Trace-Id: {{traceId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerId": "{{playerId}}",
  "sessionId": "{{sessionId}}",
  "roundId": "{{roundId}}",
  "transactionId": "t-4001",
  "amount": 1.00,
  "currency": "{{currency}}",
  "transactionType": "BET"
}

### Wallet — direct credit
POST {{host}}/api/v1/wallet/credit
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{idempotencyKey}}
X-Trace-Id: {{traceId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerId": "{{playerId}}",
  "sessionId": "{{sessionId}}",
  "roundId": "{{roundId}}",
  "transactionId": "t-4002",
  "amount": 150.00,
  "currency": "{{currency}}",
  "transactionType": "WIN"
}

### Wallet — rollback a transaction
POST {{host}}/api/v1/wallet/rollback
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{idempotencyKey}}
X-Trace-Id: {{traceId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerId": "{{playerId}}",
  "originalTransactionId": "t-4001",
  "transactionId": "t-5001",
  "rollbackReason": "DOWNSTREAM_FAILURE"
}

### Slot — init / resume session
POST {{host}}/api/v1/slot/init
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Trace-Id: {{traceId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "gameId": "{{gameId}}", "currency": "{{currency}}" }

### Slot — spin
POST {{host}}/api/v1/slot/spin
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{idempotencyKey}}
X-Trace-Id: {{traceId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "gameId": "{{gameId}}",
  "sessionId": "{{sessionId}}",
  "sessionVersion": 7,
  "betSize": 1.00,
  "powerBetActive": false
}

### Slot — start a feature (FREE_SPINS or PICK_COLLECT)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/slot/feature/start
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{idempotencyKey}}
X-Trace-Id: {{traceId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "gameId": "{{gameId}}",
  "sessionId": "{{sessionId}}",
  "sessionVersion": 8,
  "featureType": "FREE_SPINS"
}

### Slot — buy a feature
POST {{host}}/api/v1/slot/feature/buy
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{idempotencyKey}}
X-Trace-Id: {{traceId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "gameId": "{{gameId}}",
  "sessionId": "{{sessionId}}",
  "sessionVersion": 8,
  "buyType": "FREE_SPINS_BUY",
  "betSize": 1.00
}

### Slot — pick a tile
POST {{host}}/api/v1/slot/feature/pick
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{idempotencyKey}}
X-Trace-Id: {{traceId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "gameId": "{{gameId}}",
  "sessionId": "{{sessionId}}",
  "sessionVersion": 12,
  "position": 4
}

### Admin — set player wallet balance (demo profile)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/admin/wallet/balance
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Trace-Id: {{traceId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerId": "{{playerId}}",
  "currency": "{{currency}}",
  "balance": 500.00
}

### Admin — inspect a session
GET {{host}}/api/v1/admin/session/{{playerId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Trace-Id: {{traceId}}

### Admin — inspect a round
GET {{host}}/api/v1/admin/round/{{roundId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Trace-Id: {{traceId}}

### Admin — replay a round deterministically
POST {{host}}/api/v1/admin/replay/{{roundId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Trace-Id: {{traceId}}

### Admin — run RTP simulator
POST {{host}}/api/v1/admin/simulator/run
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Trace-Id: {{traceId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "gameId": "{{gameId}}",
  "mathVersion": "v1",
  "bet": 1.00,
  "spinsBaseGame": 1000,
  "spinsBonusBuyFreeSpins": 0,
  "spinsBonusBuyPickCollect": 0,
  "pickStrategy": "SEQUENTIAL"
}
